OL,3,CPatient who bit security guard denied
OL,4,Chospital treatment for a year
OL,6,FA hospital has revealed that a violent
OL,7,Fpatient who bit a security guard had
OL,8,Fhis treatment withdrawn for 12 months.
OL,10,FChesterfield Royal Hospital released
OL,11,FCCTV footage of security staff
OL,12,Fgrappling with the man in a corridor
OL,13,Fafter he became aggressive in June
OL,14,Flast year.
OL,16,FIt comes as the hospital launched a
OL,17,Fcrackdown on violence following a rise
OL,18,Fin incidents.
