OL,3,CPatient who bit security guard denied
OL,4,Chospital treatment for a year
OL,6,FThe hospital's chief executive Dr Hal
OL,7,FSpencer said the majority of patients
OL,8,Fwere civil, but the trust always
OL,9,Freported incidents to police.
OL,11,F"In the worst cases it will result in
OL,12,Four staff being unwell as a result
OL,13,Fbecause of stress and anxiety. You
OL,14,Fshouldn't come to work fearing for
OL,15,Fyour safety," he said.
OL,17,FSenior nurse Lisa Blackwell, who has
OL,18,Fworked at the hospital for 15 years,
OL,19,Fhas been punched, kicked, spat on and
OL,20,Fpushed.
