OL,6,F"It's 24/7 that it's happening," she
OL,7,Fsaid. "And it's not a case of it being
OL,8,Fa young drunk man during the night -
OL,9,Fit can be a middle-aged woman.
OL,11,F"When I was spat on it was by a 16-
OL,12,Fyear-old girl who wasn't under the
OL,13,Finfluence of anything."
OL,15,FThe Chesterfield Royal Hospital NHS
OL,16,FFoundation Trust said 14 incidents
OL,17,Fwere reported last year and resulted
OL,18,Fin police action, ranging from
OL,19,Fcommunity service to drug
OL,20,Frehabilitation orders and even a
OL,21,Fprison sentence.
