OL,6,FA staff survey revealed that 19% of
OL,7,Fstaff had experienced physical
OL,8,Fviolence at work.
OL,10,FThey included Sister Emily Gledstone,
OL,11,Fwho said she had been targeted several
OL,12,Ftimes but was most shocked by the
OL,13,Ffirst incident.
OL,15,F"A woman who was HIV positive threw
OL,16,Fher blood over me and said she wanted
OL,17,Fto poison me," she said.
OL,19,F"It affected me - I had time off work
OL,20,F- and my family. I had to have tests.
OL,21,FIt was upsetting and it scared me."
